      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">505.504</ph> Use of advertising agencies.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The services of commercial advertising agencies may be used only if the contracting officer determines that the services rendered by those agencies can either:</p>
         <ol id="d130e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d128e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>  Increase competition for contracts; or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d128e29">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>  Improve the effectiveness of GSA advertising and marketing programs.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
